://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPaDUjB.png&h=1d5597b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw,唔講其他，佢d野食都好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"得 唔撚食"},{"pid":"4ba8b0ffaa061edc6a3658b2cdf33fcb82a3c41e","tid":1433494,"uid":217415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d285087456c51271a4c08a809206fc5c4855e4cf","tid":1433494,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"我住果頭,好彩冇食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人認為佢隔黎果間西餐幾高質<br />\n不過講真呀,香港大部份老細都藍屍黎嫁啦特別係中式/港式<br />\n爭在有冇大聲講俾你聽既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"大聲講就係自己攞黎衰"},{"pid":"a3e1e1c4d088fa527255ae7fefa35f0bd4fd574e","tid":1433494,"uid":22323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b425478f0e1066e15e0fec534810e81b15476d0","tid":1433494,"uid":96780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8234cbfdc02f8698209d5765db98e06e9d6ea439","tid":1433494,"uid":283788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a32876f4d10bb47877e2085677f5ab72fb3aa811","tid":1433494,"uid":96780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:23:22.000Z","msg":"樓主無話過侍應支持亂打人同濫權<br />\n又起度歪曲事實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"講話比人入差館輪，話撐警<br />\n而家警察濫捕，亂打人仲撐佢地，咁都唔算支持佢地？<br />\n你d思想都幾特別？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:09:51.000Z","msg":"又黎偏激言論<br />\n你估全世界都好似連燈仔當所有警察都係黑警咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"個老板話個女仔比人入去比人輪都抵"},{"pid":"fb2727f966f44b7cccb654cd911c9509e6a34411","tid":1433494,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo